Group Events
Want that perfect beach wedding?
Are you looking for the right spot for a business meeting?
You found just the right place.

Contact our restaurant manager for more information.
Ask us about hosting your next function.
We understand that not all groups are traditional…
Whether you’re bringing the entire family for your daughter’s or granddaughter’s Sweet 16, or a Holiday party  we’ve got everything you could ask for to make your event unforgettable. Below are just a few of our most popular event types. Use these topic’s to get ideas, but never hesitate to ask about your unique event. With just a short conversation and some planning, we’ll have you celebrating in no time!
Social Events
From Bar/Bat Mitzvahs and Sweet Sixteens to Anniversaries and Birthdays, we’ve done it all and can’t wait to help plan yours .
Reunions & Social Gatherings
Reunions are a special time and we want to be sure your entire family is taken care of. From beautiful Beaches  and Ocean front decks to fully catered meals and personal concierges, we’re here to make sure your family gathering is all about family. Leave the details to us!
Business and Company Events
Whether its a company holiday party, a retirement party or an awards dinner theres no better place to have it than on the ocean at Havana jacks Oceanside. We have custom menus to fit all occasions. We will help you plan your event from start to finish with creative ideas that will make your company proud. Let us help you celebrate the most important asset your company has, your employees, by providing an experience they will all cherish and you can be proud of.
For more information, including catering menus, please call us at
(305)587-3807
.

Weddings and Events
Want that perfect beach wedding?
Are you looking for the right spot for a business meeting?
You found just the right place.

Contact our restaurant manager for more information.
Ask us about hosting your next function.
Come on, you know you have thought about it endlessly! When it comes to planning your Big Day, it has to be memorable, wonderfully romantic and uniquely crafted to you and the love of your life. We know you are excited about your wedding and have many ideas about what you want – but let’s face it: planning a destination island wedding with lots of different vendors can be quite stressful and time consuming.  Havana Jacks Ocean view restaurant and bar offers dramatic, breathtaking, ocean views for a festive reception with outstanding cuisine, beverages and service.
While Glunz Ocean Beach Hotel & Resort is only footsteps away offering a private beach, sunset pier or crystal blue pool to hold your unforgettable ceremony at. Conclude with our island themed oceanfront lodging for you and your guests to enjoy, and you have the perfect destination wedding from start to finish. We are located in the Heart of the Florida Keys on Key Colony Beach. In recent years, we have become a truly unique wedding venue with world class beachfront romance.
We will help plan every detail of your wedding day, from your first visit to the last dance at your reception. Our experienced wedding professionals and favorite preferred vendors will take care of all of your wedding needs, allowing you to be relaxed so you can enjoy your special day.To explore your options and learn more about our wedding venue and packages, contact us to set up an appointment and come see for yourself why our private beachfront hotel & restaurant in Key Colony Beach, Florida is such a special place. Please contact us at
1-305-587-9807
for more information.

About Us
About us
Havana Jack's
Havana Jack’s is a breath of fresh air at water’s edge Unique in every aspect from our location to our menu, we are far from the traditional calamari and shrimp cocktail type restaurant. Every chowder and sauce is made in house daily, and paired with seafood straight from sea to the dock to us, it’s so fresh we print it each and every day on our chalkboard menu.
Creative culinary innovation has resulted in presenting a variety of scrumptious dishes that are distinctly our own. Experience the highest fresh food standards supported by our Caribbean, Havana, and American infused dishes that have been creatively designed. Feast on such delights as our Sautéed Crab Cakes, Grouper Oscar, nightly fresh fish specials and Steaks. The view from our Tiki Bar, restaurant and patio deck overlooking the Atlantic Ocean speaks for itself. Wonder out on our pier and experience what the locals call the million dollar view.The plush outdoor oceanfront patio is reminiscent of a tropical retreat offering picturesque locations for guests to mingle, dance, sip cocktails and smoke fine tableside cut cigars. Our restaurant, bar and lounge are open
11am-11:00pm
Wednesday through Sunday. Spend the afternoon at Havana Jacks with a specialty mojito in one hand, a fine cigar in the other, while enjoying a stunning view of the Atlantics turquoise water. From our exclusive on the water ambiance to our incredibly fresh and delicious food and beverage offerings, Havana Jacks has it all. Great food, drinks, and entertainment to enjoy with friends.
Patio & Lounge Area
Havana Jack’s is a breath of fresh air at water’s edge Unique in every aspect from our location to our menu, we are far from the traditional calamari and shrimp cocktail type restaurant. Every chowder and sauce is made in house daily, and paired with seafood straight from sea to the dock to us, it’s so fresh we print it each and every day on our chalkboard menu.
Live Entertainment
Always tasteful, our entertainment includes interactive customer entertainment ranging from acoustic performances, DJ’s, trivia, and other live events. Our entertainment includes a wide variety of music, guest participation, high energy and sheer excitement! Havana Jacks is one of the best casual fine dining and entertainment lounges in the Keys, if not in the country.
Staff
Our educated bartenders and customer staff team members always enjoy interacting with our guests and have a vast knowledge of every menu offering. Our guests will frequently be asked to taste various rums or sample some unique blended wines; our team will be your tour guide taking your taste buds on a much needed vacation from the norm, not only providing sufficient information to elevate the guests experience, but also allowing our valued visitors with the opportunity to expand their own knowledge.
